main event: On February 6, 1965, multiple photographs of unidentified spherical objects were documented in Liberty, Ohio.
interesting points: The report references 19 unclassified photographs of various spherical objects,Some photographs depict the objects with measurement scales for size reference,One witness, Harold Huffman, reported seeing two disc-shaped objects on September 27, 1965,The objects were described as silver-colored and rotating,The report indicates that local police received multiple calls about similar sightings in the area.
witness description: Mr. Harold Huffman observed the objects from his property
